## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Set environment variables
export LLM_PROVIDER=bedrock          # or anthropic, openai, ollama
export BEDROCK_MODEL_ID=anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-20250514-v1:0
export BEDROCK_REGION=ap-southeast-2

# Run the agent
uvicorn {{packageName}}.app:app --reload --port 8000
```

